name: Beeez
description:
This embedding was trained on 140 high quality close-up pictures of Bees.

Without much prompting it will deliver you endless pictures of bees collecting nectar from flowers. With some creative prompting you can create bee-like creatures and machines of all sorts.

** Honey not included

You might enjoy the rest of my embugging series:

  • Araknope: Spiders

  • Beeez: Bees

  • Pmantis: Preying Mantises
